e looks good for a 94 year old man.  He will be admitted for observation and treatment.  Fortunately, it was not a heart attack or a stroke.  \r\n\r\nI am not asking for medical advise or warnings about this medication or that medication, as those types of things have been discussed incessantly on here over the last few years.  \r\n\r\nI just wanted to give an update and my heartfelt appreciation for all of the prayers and kind words.\r\n\r\nGod bless \ud83d\ude4c you all.  ", "author": "Landslide_2020", "created": 1776374472206, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ColonelKlink", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "For those that saw my earlier post about my dad being taken to the hospital by ambulance.  Thank you all for your prayers.  Here's an update I received from my sister.", "last_comment_created": 1776393895712, "content": "<p>Original post.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://patriots.win/p/1ASZR1tBgX/i-dont-know-all-of-the-specifics/\" target=\"_blank\">https://patriots.win/p/1ASZR1tBgX/i-dont-know-all-of-the-specifics/</a></p>\n<p>Update:</p>\n<p>My father has pneumonia and a high fever.  Everything else looks good for a 94 year old man.  He will be admitted for observation and treatment.  Fortunately, it was not a heart attack or a stroke.</p>\n<p>I am not asking for medical advise or warnings about this medication or that medication, as those types of things have been discussed incessantly on here over the last few years.</p>\n<p>I just wanted to give an update and my heartfelt appreciation for all of the prayers and kind words.</p>\n<p>God bless \ud83d\ude4c you all.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_